    "yg_image_with_text_list_KQztzz": {
      "type": "yg-image-with-text-list",
      "blocks": {
        "item_FQddzf": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 0,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3000W_Peak_Dual_Motors.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/3000WPeak.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>3000W Peak Dual Motors for Serious Power</p>",
            "content": "<p>Powered by 3000W peak dual motors, this electric scooter delivers the strength you need for fast starts, steep climbs, and challenging terrain. With up to 35 MPH max speed, 75 N.m torque, and a 30° max uphill capability, it gives riders powerful performance for both city streets and off-road adventures.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "Up to 25 MPH top speed",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_Y77eFc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/48V_20Ah_Long_Range_Battery.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/LongRangeBattery.png",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>960Wh Battery for Longer Adventures</p>",
            "content": "<p>Equipped with a 960Wh high-capacity battery, this scooter is designed for longer rides and fewer charging stops. The 48V 20Ah battery supports up to 70 miles max range under ideal riding conditions, while built-in over-charge protection helps support a safer and more reliable charging experience.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_yxmgJc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11_Off-Road_Pneumatic_Tires.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/1671a0c5660ebfea60f6f53afe73f20a_2257f4b6-7427-4912-83c4-8809eef516dd.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>11\" Off-Road Pneumatic Tires for All-Terrain Control</p>",
            "content": "<p>Large 11-inch off-road pneumatic tires provide enhanced grip, shock absorption, and stability across multiple surfaces. Whether you're riding through city streets, mountain paths, sand roads, or gravel trails, the deep-tread tire design helps improve traction and control.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_4A6yqg": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Rear_Shock_Absorbers.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/Front_RearShock.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>Front & Rear Dual Shock Absorbers</p>",
            "content": "<p>The front and rear shock absorption system helps reduce impact from bumps, rocks, potholes, and rough terrain. Combined with the large off-road tires, it delivers a smoother, more comfortable ride with better stability on uneven roads.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_qBUgpX": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Dual_Disc_Brakes.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/2DiscBrakes.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>Dual Disc Brake System for Stronger Stopping Power</p>",
            "content": "<p>Equipped with front and rear disc brakes, this scooter delivers stronger and more responsive stopping power than a single-disc brake setup. The dual brake system helps improve braking efficiency and gives riders better control during high-speed riding, downhill sections, and sudden stops.</p>",
